column1: Baby Barnaby's////It's a restaurant in a cute little house
column2: so it has a very warm feeling. I like the California vibe inside with all of the points of interests up on the wall. There is also seating in the patio
column3: which is nice when it isn't too hot outside. They usually have complimentary coffee outside
column4: and this is great on days when there is a wait (usually around 30 minutes max). It is definitely worth the wait though. They are dog friendly too.
